			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Charleston</placeName> <date>9<hi rend="sup">th</hi> of December 1852</date></p>
			<p><addressee>Mr. Isaac Leeser</addressee>&#59;</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)">Dear Sir&#59;</p>
          <p rend="indent(5)">Encouraged by<lb/> the following sentence on the 356<hi rend="sup">th</hi> page of the<lb/> Occident of <date>October</date> last. &#8220;Of course we give only<lb/> <persName>Mr. M&#39;s</persName> own statements&#44; and should there be any<lb/> mistake&#44; we will cheerfully insert a reply&#59; our<lb/> only object being to do justice in the premises&#44; and<lb/> to charge no one with wrong&#45;doing&#44; without the fullest<lb/> proof.&#8221; I therefore send you this article to be pub&#61;<lb/>lished in the Occident in reply to one of <persName>Mr. Mar&#61;<lb/>cussohn</persName> of <date>October</date> last&#59; and I feel confident&#44; that<lb/> you will do us the favour and the justice&#44; <del>that you</del><lb/> to fulfill a promise made so public&#59; all we ask<lb/> is justice &#38; no more. I do not wish&#44; unless<lb/> compelled&#44; to say or write any more about this<lb/> matter&#44; but desire to live in harmony &#38; peace.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">However should you refuse to publish this<lb/> communication&#44; though I have not the slightest<lb/> idea that you will&#44; for you love justice as well as<lb/> myself&#44; I shall be necessitated to vindicate the<lb/> conduct of the Jewish mission society&#44; in reference<lb/> to this matter&#44; not only in the Jewish Chronicle<lb/> but also in the public journals of this &#38; other cities<lb/> where Jews are&#44; &#38; our mission society is represented.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Yours very sincerely</p>
          <p rend="indent(4)"><persName role="author">G. D. Bernheim</persName></p>
          
          <div>
            <p><ref target="Occident_PDFs/Occ_10_7.pdf">The above text refers to Occident Volume 10 No. 7 page 356. Click here to view.</ref></p>
          </div>
